title: US Avoids to Cope With Russia Against ISIL Fearing to Lose Credibility
text: The White House refrains from cooperation with Russia in fighting the Islamic State over fears of losing its face after waging a propaganda war against Russia and Syrian President Bashar Assad, a member of the Syrian Social Nationalist Party told Sputnik Wednesday. ...
